अ
2. अ (ut mihi videtur, a praec. v. gr. comp. 371.) particula<BR>negativa, quae vocabulis praefigitur per compositionem.<BR>Ante vocales ei additur न् euphonicum (v. gr. 114, 667<BR>et cf. gr. ἀ, ἀν, lat. in, goth. et germ. un).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=001-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2" target="_blank">Correction</a>

