अगाध (secundum Wils. BAH. ex अ priv. et गाध locus, situs<BR>cf. nostrum Boden-los. Derivari etiam potest a rad.<BR>गाह् submergi, quae primitive गाध् sonuisse videtur,<BR>v. gr. comp. 23.) valde profundus. N. 6.13. — (Huc<BR>fortasse pertinent gr. ἀγαϑός et goth. gôths (Th. gôda,<BR>abjecto a initiali) sicut scr. वरीयस् melior, वरिष्ठ optimus<BR>cum उरु magnus, latus cohaerent; v. gr. comp. 298.).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=002-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=51" target="_blank">Correction</a>

