2. अड् 5. P. (व्यापने) occupare.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=005-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=128" target="_blank">Correction</a>

