अणीयस् (ab अणु s. comp. ईयस्) minor, parvulus, perexiguus.<BR>BH. 8.9.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=005-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=133" target="_blank">Correction</a>

