अतिशयम् (ex अति et शय a r. शी jacere s. अ) ultra modum,<BR>abundanter, effuse. UR. 91.3.infr.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=152" target="_blank">Correction</a>

