अतिसर्ज
अतिसर्ज m. (r. सृज् dimittere praef. अति s. अ) donatio.<BR>A. 5.53. RAGH. 10.43.; cf. अतिसर्जन.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=154" target="_blank">Correction</a>

