अतीव
अतीव (ex अति et इव sicut, hic pleon.) valde. IN. 5.9.<BR>N. 1.13.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=156" target="_blank">Correction</a>

