अत्यय
अत्यय m. (r. इ, praef. अति s. अ) discessus, abitio, inde<BR>obitus, mors; cum तप calor: तपात्यय caloris discessus<BR>vel obitus, inde secundum HEM. pluviosum anni<BR>tempus. SAK. 49.5.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=161" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्यर्थम्
अत्यर्थम् (AVY. ex अति et अर्थ m. res) ultra modum. SU. 3.25.<BR>N. 11.20.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=162" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्र
अत्र (a stirpe pronominali अ - gr. 270. - s. त्र) hic, illic.<BR>In lingua scenica saepe praefigitur voci भवत् et ejus<BR>fem. भवती.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=163" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अत्रि
अत्रि m. hostis, inimicus, adversarius.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=164" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अथ
अथ (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe pronominali अ suff. थ sicut<BR>कथम् a क)<BR>1) at, in initio sententiae. N. 2.28. 5.1.<BR>2) et, etiam. IN. 1.18. 2.13. BR. 2.3.<BR>3) tunc, illo tempore.<BR>SU. 4.15. H. 1.21. 22., confer तदा.<BR>4) deinde,<BR>tum, post. N. 1.25. SU. 1.18.<BR>5) explet. praecipue ante<BR>वा q. v. (lat. at).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=165" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अथवा
अथवा (अथ + वा)<BR>1) vel, sive, saepissime.<BR>2) attamen.<BR>SAK. 8.5. HIT. 23.1.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=006-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=166" target="_blank">Correction</a>

