अस्
2. अस् 2. P. (ATM. solum in conjunctione cum व्यति, irr.<BR>v. gr. 365, 366, 367, 457, 458.)<BR>1) esse, existere. BH. 2.12. 66.<BR>H. 1.39. SU. 1.25.<BR>2) esse, ut verbum abstractum<BR>vel copulativum. SU. 1.21. SA. 4.7.<BR>3) fieri. A. 8.14.<BR>(Lith. es-mi, es-ti; slav. jes-mj, jes-tj; gr. ἐμ-μί, ἐσ-τί,<BR>prius per assimilationem ex ἐσ-μί; lat. sum, es-t;<BR>goth. i-m, ex is-m, is-t; nostrum is-t.).<BR>c. प्रादुर् (manifesto, palam. gr. 685.) apparere, in conspectum<BR>venire, oriri. A. 4.8. 6.16. 8.13.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=024-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=756" target="_blank">Correction</a>

अस्
3. अस् 4. P. deponere, abjicere. NALOD. 4.36.<BR>c. अप<BR>1) id. NALOD. 3.8.<BR>2) relinquere, deserere. HIT. 107.5.<BR>3) postponere, negligere. HIT. 70.10.<BR>c. अभि exercere, tractare, versari in alqâre. SAK. 32.infr.<BR>c. उत् praef. वि (व्युदस्) i. q. simpl. BH. 18.51.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) deponere. DR. 1.5. 7.8. SA. 5.9.<BR>c. वि + नि ponere, deponere, collocare. N. 24.45. RAM. ed. Ser. III.47.7. 70.5.<BR>c. सम् + नि deponere. SA. 3.18. BH. 3.30. 4.41. 5.13.<BR>c. निस् ejicere. DEV. 1.18.<BR>c. वि part. व्यस्त consternatus, confusus, dejectus. A. 10.64.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=024-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=757" target="_blank">Correction</a>

