इत्
इत् ut mihi videtur, neutrum stirpis pronominalis ई, quod<BR>in dialecto Vêd. aliis tertiae personae pronominibus adjungitur;<BR>v. Addenda ad gr. cr. 270. et gr. comp. 360.<BR>(Lat. id, goth. ita, germ. vet. iz, nostrum es).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1115" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतर
इतर (a stirpe pronominali इ s. तर, gr. 277.) alius. BH. 3.21.<BR>(lat. iterum, v. gr. comp. 292.; hib. itir id.).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1116" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतरेतर
इतरेतर (ex इतर + इतर, sensu et constructione cum<BR>अन्योन्य q. v. convenit, a quo in formatione eo solum<BR>dissidet, quod prius इतर, quanquam nominativum exprimat,<BR>vera vocis stirps est, nisi इतरेतर in {#itarA +<BR>itara#} dissolvere mavis, ita ut, quod mihi magis placet,<BR>prius compositi membrum Nominat. fem. sit, qui aliorum<BR>generum quoque vice fungatur) i. q. अन्योन्य q. v.<BR>A. 9.16.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1117" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतस्
इतस् Adv. (a stirpe pronominali इ s. तस् gr. 652.)<BR>1) hinc,<BR>ab hoc loco. N. 2.13. 12.121. 18.18. BH. 14.1.<BR>2) in<BR>comparativis constructionibus saepe ablativi अस्मात् substantive<BR>positi locum tenet. H. 1.5. BH. 5.7.<BR>3) ante ततस्,<BR>aut इतस् repetitum, interposito च, accusativi, directionem<BR>versus locum exprimentis, vel locativi vim habet,<BR>et tum prius इतस् significat huc vel hîc, posterius<BR>illuc vel illic. N. 10.4. 11.13. 19. DR. 8.25. Etiam<BR>semel positum इतस् interdum huc et hîc significat.<BR>SAK. 8.9. 40.10.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1118" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इति
इति Adv. (ut equidem puto, a stirpe pronom. इ s. ति) sic.<BR>BH. 18.78. UR. 16. Saepissime hoc adverbium, aut supplendo<BR>aut apposito verbo dicere vel cogitare, usurpatur<BR>ad indicandum sermonem vel cogitationem directe<BR>introductam, et plerumque introducta verba sequitur,<BR>nonnunquam etiam eis interponitur. H. 4.21. BR. 3.4.<BR>SU. 1.23. 32. SA. 1.23. DR. 1.10. 7.27. A. 9.30. 31. RAM. ed. Ser. III.44.12. 14.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1119" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिकर्तव्यता
इतिकर्तव्यता f. (Abstractum vocis इतिकर्तव्य sic faciendum<BR>s. ता) rei faciendae status. SA. 3.7. HIT. 42.9.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1120" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिमात्र
इतिमात्र (BAH. e praec. et मात्र n. mensura, modis) talem<BR>mensuram i. e. qualitatem, conditionem habens, talis.<BR>BR. 3.1.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1121" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इतिहास
इतिहास m. narratio, historia ex antiquissimo tempore.<BR>SU. 1.1. (Ut videtur, ex इति sic, expletivo ह et आस<BR>fuit, quod hac in compositione substantivi naturam assumsit.).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=038-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1122" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्थम्
इत्थम् (ex perdito Neutro इत् = lat. id - quod hac in formatione<BR>Thematis loco fungitur - v. gr. 263. - s. थम् cui<BR>respondet lat. tem in i-tem, au-tem, gr. comp. 425.) sic,<BR>ita. SAK. 50.4. HIT. 75.6.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=039-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1123" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्यर्थम्
इत्यर्थम् Adv. (ex इति sic et अर्थम् propter) ideo, hanc<BR>ob causam. BR. 3.4.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=039-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1124" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इत्वर
