इल्
इल्<BR>1) 6. P. (गतौ K. शये गतौ क्षेपे V.) ire; jaculari; jacere,<BR>cubare.<BR>2) 10. P. (प्रेरणे K. क्षेपे V.) mittere; jaculari.<BR>(Germ. vet. îllu, îllo - per assimil. ex îlju - no strum<BR>eile; cambro-brit. il progressio, motus; gr. ἐλάω.<BR>Radix sanscr. orta esse videtur ex अर् - v. ऋ - mutato<BR>र् in ल् et अ attenuato in इ, eâdem ratione quâ supra<BR>इट् ex अट् explicavimus.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=040-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1156" target="_blank">Correction</a>

इला
