ऋत्
ऋत् 1. P. (स्पर्धनैश्वर्यघृणागतिषु) ire; aemulari, certare;<BR>imperare; vituperare. (Haec radix orta esse videtur<BR>ex ऋ - अर् - adjecto त्. Huc retulerim rad. goth.<BR>LITH ire - leitha, laith, lithum - mutato r in l et litteris<BR>transpositis pro ilth ex alth, arth, attenuato a in i, sicut<BR>in r. KIN germinare = जन्; hib. rith «course, flight,<BR>gallop, race», rithim «I run, range, strull, rush».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=056-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1604" target="_blank">Correction</a>

ऋत
