ऋभुक्षिन्
ऋभुक्षिन् m. (Nom. ऋभुक्षास् a Th. ऋभुक्षस्, reliqui casus<BR>fortes, Vocativo excepto, descendunt a Th. ऋभुक्षन्,<BR>debilissimi casus a ऋभुक्ष्) cognomen Indri.<BR>AM.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=057-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=1621" target="_blank">Correction</a>

