कृच्छ्र
कृच्छ्र (ut mihi videtur, e कृत् vel कृत abjecto अ et zra e<BR>श्रम abjectâ syllabâ finali)<BR>1) difficilis, molestus, aerumnosus.<BR>2) n. difficultas, onus, molestia, miseria. H. 1.15.<BR>BR. 3.11. N. 15.16. 24.18.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=080-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2349" target="_blank">Correction</a>

