कृषिन् m. (r. कृष् s. इन्) arator. SU. 2.24.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=083-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2388" target="_blank">Correction</a>

