क्रोष्टु m. (Nom. क्रोष्टा a th. क्रोष्टृ, 181.) canis aureus, anglice<BR>jackal. DR. 1.17.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=089-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2505" target="_blank">Correction</a>

क्रोष्टृ
क्रोष्टृ v. क्रोष्टु et gr. 181.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=089-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2506" target="_blank">Correction</a>

क्रौञ्च
क्रौञ्च m. nomen avis, ardeae species; Wils. «a Kind of heron<BR>or curlew». R. Schl. I.2.12.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=089-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2507" target="_blank">Correction</a>

