क्लन्द्
क्लन्द् 1. P. (आह्वानरोदनयोः; grammatici scribunt क्लद्,<BR>gr. 110^a).) clamare, ejulare, flere. (Cf. {#klad, krad,<BR>krand#}; hib. glaodhaim «I call, bawl, roar, shout».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=089-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2511" target="_blank">Correction</a>

