क्षय m. (r. क्षि s. अ)<BR>1) occasus, interitus, exitium. H. 4.48.<BR>BR. 2.20. N. 26.12.<BR>2) domus, domicilium, sedes,<BR>praesertim deorum. H. 1.47. M. 1.2510.: {#nirjagAma kzayAn<BR>narAyaRasya#}; R. Schl. II.6.27.: {#indrakzayasanniBam<BR>puram#}. (Hib. cai domus.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=092-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2563" target="_blank">Correction</a>

