क्षाम
क्षाम (r. क्षै s. म pro त vel न)<BR>1) emaciatus, macer. BHAR. 1.63.:<BR>क्षुधाक्षाम. UP. 27.<BR>2) tenuis, gracilis. BHAR. 1.92.<BR>3) debilis. Lass. 11.14.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=093-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2573" target="_blank">Correction</a>

