क्षुद् 7. P. A. क्षुणद्मि, क्षुन्दे contundere, conterere. Part.<BR>pass. क्षुण्ण. DEV. 3.24.: खुरक्षुण्णमहीतलः; 9.35.: दंष्ट्राक्षुण्णशिरोधर.<BR>(Fortasse huc pertinet gr. ξύω, ξέω<BR>pro ξεύω, adjecto Gunnae incremento; si ita est, sibilans<BR>in formis ξυσ-τός, ξεσ-τός ad radicem pertinet,<BR>mutato, ex generali euphoniae lege, δ in σ. Lith. skaus-ti<BR>dolet, e skaud-ti, skaudếjimas dolor; pra-skunda dolere<BR>incipit, nu-skaudinu noceo, transposito ks in sk.)<BR>c. वि id. DEV. 3.25.: वेगभ्रमणविक्षुण्णा मही.<BR>c. सम् id. RAM. III.63.10.: {#babanDur banDanIyAMSca kzodyAn<BR>saYckzudus taTA#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=094-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2594" target="_blank">Correction</a>

