खन् 1. P. fodere, perfodere. HIT. 30.1.: {#mama vivaraN<BR>KanitvA#}; RAM. I.32.52.: पृथिवी सर्वा खन्यते. Part.<BR>pass. खात, gr. 616.; Gerund. in य, खन्य vel खाय;<BR>Pass. खन्ये vel खाये. (Gr. χαίνω, χανῶ, germ. vet.<BR>ginêm, ginôm hio, nostrum gähne, anglo-sax. cina<BR>rima, cinan hiare; lat. cuniculus, canalis; v. खनि, खानि.)<BR>c. उत् effodere. BHAR. 3.5.: उत्खातन् निधिशङ्कयाक्षितितलम्;<BR>evellere, eruere. RAGH. 4.36.: {#vaNgAn<BR>utKAya…nOsADanodDatAn . nicaKAna jayasTamBAn<BR>gaNgaSreto'ntarezu saH#}; ubi उत्खन् effodere opponitur<BR>verbo निखन् infodere, defodere, hî infodiendo<BR>erigere; Schol. Calc. उत्खाय explicat per उत्पाट्य.<BR>c. उत् praef. प्र id. RAM. I.32.40.: {#protKananta ekEkayojanam<BR>BUmeH#}.<BR>c. नि infodere, defodere. HIT. 124.16.: {#niKanyante hfdaye<BR>SokaSaNkavaH#}; RAGH. 4.36.; v. खन् praef. उत्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=096-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2657" target="_blank">Correction</a>

