गर्ज्
1. गर्ज् 1. P. A. clamare, strepere, crepare, increpare. H. 4.36.<BR>M. 41.; part. pass. गर्जित n. clamor, strepitus.<BR>H. 4.13. (Cf. गॄ, गिर्, गर्द्; lat. garrio assimilatione e<BR>gargio explicari possit; fortasse etiam gurges huc pertinet,<BR>ita ut ab aquae strepitu dictus sit, sicut M. 41. de mari<BR>legitur: गर्जमानम् इवा ऽम्भसा; germ. vet. kurran<BR>garrire, strepere, stridere, (nostrum quarren, girren),<BR>krago (e kargo) gula, kragil garrulus, krachôn crepare;<BR>mutatis rr in ll: gellan tinnire, ar-gellan insonare, kallôn,<BR>challôn clamare, effari, challônte garriens, kallari<BR>verbosus (Graff III.178. 383.); gr. ἀγγέλλω, quod<BR>Thierschius ex ἀναγέλλω explicat.)<BR>c. अभि acclamare. M. 1.1184.: परस्परम् भृशम् अभिगर्जताम्.<BR>c. प्रति reclamare, repugnare. RAGH. 9.9.: {#nideSam alaNGayatAm<BR>aBUt suhfd, ayohfdayaH pratigarjatAm#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=102-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2769" target="_blank">Correction</a>

