घट्ट्
घट्ट् 1. A. 10. P. (चलने K. चाले V.) movere, commovere,<BR>वीणाम् विघट्टितुम् lyram pulsare. MR. 20.3.<BR>Cf. घट्.<BR>c. वि<BR>1) movere, commovere. BHAR. 3.36.: वायुविघट्टिताभ्रपटली.<BR>2) aperire. MAH. 2.1674.: {#dvAram…<BR>viGawwayan karAByAm#}.<BR>c. सम् terere, conterere, fricare. RAGH. 6.73.: {#saNGawwayann<BR>aNgadam aNgadena#} (Schol. घर्षयन्).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=113-1b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2975" target="_blank">Correction</a>

