घन (ut videtur, a हन् s. अ, mutato ह् in घ्, v. gr. 357.)<BR>1) crassus, pinguis, turgidus. Lass. 6.8.: घनैर् वृक्षैः;<BR>ĆAUR. 15.: घनेरुदेशे; GITA-GOV. 10.6.: घनजघनमण्डले.<BR>2) impervius, impenetrabilis. RAGH. 8.90.: {#vacaH…alabDapadaM<BR>hfdi SokaGane pratiyAtam#} (Schol.<BR>निविडे); 11.18.: {#cakAra vivaraM SilAGane tAqakorasi<BR>sa rAmasAyakaH#} (Schol. निविडे).<BR>3) Subst. m. nubes.<BR>RAM. I.29.14.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=113-1b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=2980" target="_blank">Correction</a>

