चिकुर m. (ut videtur, forma redupl. a quapiam in र् vel,<BR>quod ad idem redit, in ऋ, ॠ desinente radice; fortasse<BR>a चर् e कर्, ita ut crinis a mobilitate sit nominatus; cf.<BR>चञ्चुर्, चङ्कुर; sive a कॄ) crinis. (Cf. gr. ϰίϰιννος,<BR>quod assimilatione e ϰίϰιϱνος explicari posset; lat. cincinnus,<BR>quod syllabâ redupl. cum scr. चञ्चुर् convenit;<BR>cirrus.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=124-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3165" target="_blank">Correction</a>

