चिन्तापर
चिन्तापर Adj. (BAH. e praec. et पर n. praecipuum, eximium,<BR>optimum, v. gr. 666.) cogitationem tanquam excellentissimum<BR>habens, in cogitatione defixus, cogitatione absorptus.<BR>N. 2.2. RAM. I.34.34.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=125-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3189" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चिर
