चिरस्य Adv. (Gen. a चिर) post longum tempus, tandem,<BR>denique. H. 2.8. 9.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=125-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3193" target="_blank">Correction</a>

