चिरात् Adv. (Ablat, a चिर) id. RAGH. 11.63. (Schol. बहुकालेन);<BR>12.87.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=125-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3194" target="_blank">Correction</a>

