चिल्
चिल् 6. P. (वसने K. वासे V.) vestire. (V. चेल et cf.<BR>hib. ceilim «I conceal, hide, cover», caille «a veil or<BR>cowl»; lat. celare, fortasse etiam velum, velare, quae e<BR>quelum, quelare explicaverim, sicut vermis e quermis, v.<BR>कृमि; germ. vet. hilu celo, a rad. HAL, quod nititur<BR>formâ gunatâ चेल्, abjecto i; helm galea, heliu velo, heli<BR>velamentum; goth. hulja occulo; lat. oc-culo.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=125-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3199" target="_blank">Correction</a>

