चीर्ण scissus, divisus, trop. impletus, solutus, de votis (a r.<BR>चॄ descendere videtur, non tamen haec syllaba a grammaticis<BR>inter radices recepta est). RAM. I.18.5.; SA. 6.12. 41.<BR>(lege चीर्णानि, चीर्णं. - Cf. चिरि, चूर्ण, कॄ, जॄ.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=125-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3211" target="_blank">Correction</a>

