चूचुक
चूचुक m. n. (etiam चुचुक, forma reduplicata, ut videtur, a<BR>चूष् bibere, sicut gr. ϑηλή, τίτϑη, τιτϑός, nec non<BR>nostrum Zitze, cum धे bibere (cf. ϑῆσϑαι) cohaerent,<BR>et lat. papilla tanquam forma redupl. ad पातुम्, po-tum,<BR>reduci posset) papilla. UR. 84.1. ĆAUR. 14. (Hib. cioch<BR>mamma, fortasse etiam coicht «children» huc pertinet.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=127-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3238" target="_blank">Correction</a>

चूडा
चूडा f.<BR>1) vertex, culmen, cacumen, praesertim capitis vertex.<BR>RAGH. 17.28. HIT. 55.19.<BR>2) cincinnus singulus<BR>in vertice. RAGH. 18.50.<BR>3) crista.<BR>4) caput. Wils.<BR>(Cf. कूट et hib. cuit caput.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=127-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3239" target="_blank">Correction</a>

