चूष्
चूष् 1. P. sugere, चोष्य sugendus. MAH. 2.316.: {#lehyaY<BR>cozyaYca peyaYca#}. (Fortasse चूष् e चुक्ष्, ejecto क्, mutilatum<BR>est, cf. चुचुक, चूचुक; चुक्ष् autem e quadam<BR>simpliciore radice in gutturalem vel palatalem desinente<BR>deducendum esset, sicut धिक्ष् accendere a दह्, भक्ष्<BR>edere a भग्, vel भज्, cf. ϕάγω et भुज्; res si ita se<BR>habet, cum चूष्, e चुक्, et चुचुक papilla contulerim<BR>lat. sugo et succus, mutatâ initiali gutturali in sibilantem,<BR>nostrum saugen, gr. ὑγϱός.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=127-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3244" target="_blank">Correction</a>

