1. चृत् 6. P. (हिंसायाम् K. हिंसे ग्रन्थे V.) offendere, laedere,<BR>occidere; cf. कृत्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=127-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3245" target="_blank">Correction</a>

