चेत्
चेत् Conj. (ut equidem puto, e च et इत् q. v.) si, postponitur.<BR>BR. 2.17. N. 17.29. R. Schl. II.8.34. - Cum antecedente<BR>यदि<BR>1) si quidem. R. Schl. II.8.34.b.: {#yadi ced<BR>Barato DarmAt pitryaM rAjyam avApsyati#}.<BR>2) etsi,<BR>etiamsi. MAH. 1.4203.: {#yady asti ced DanaM sarvam<BR>vfTABogA Bavantu tAH#}. (Gr. ϰαί.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=127-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3251" target="_blank">Correction</a>

