छुर्
छुर् 6. P. (छेदे K. लोपे V.) findere, abscindere. (Cf. {#Kur,<BR>kft, Cid#}; hib. scuirim vel sguirim «I cease, desist»<BR>= छुरामि; ita lat. finis - pro fidnis? - cum findo cohaerere<BR>videtur; v. छेद cessatio, finis; huc etiam trahi possent<BR>scaoilim, scairim et spialaim, quae supra cum छिद्<BR>comparavimus; germ. vet. SCAR tondere, secare, sciru,<BR>scar, scârumês, nostrum Schere, quae nituntur formâ<BR>छर्, unde fortasse छुर् attenuato a in u; SCAR etiam<BR>e छेद् explicari posset, ejecto posteriore diphthongi ए<BR>elemento, et mutato d in r.)<BR>c. वि perfundere, diffundere, spargere, dispergere. ĆAUR. 12.:<BR>आस्यम्…श्रमजलस्फुटसान्द्रविन्दुमुक्ताफलप्रकरविच्छुरितम्<BR>(Schol. व्याप्तम्); UR. 78.9.: {#sPuratA<BR>vicCuritam idaM (te muKam) rAgeRa maRer lalAwanihitasya#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=132-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3318" target="_blank">Correction</a>

