जटुल
जटुल m. (r. जट् s. उल) macula, nota in corpore. AM.: =<BR>पिप्लु.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=133-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3351" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जठर
जठर m. venter. H. 2.3. (Goth. qvithrs, Th. qvithra in<BR>comp. lausqvithrs inanem ventrem habens, quithus uterus;<BR>fortasse lat. venter e guenter, insertâ nasali.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=133-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3352" target="_blank">Correction</a>

जड
जड<BR>1) frigidus.<BR>2) hebetatus, obtusus, conturbatus, mente<BR>captus, stolidus, stupidus. UR. 7.9. RAGH. 8.74. BHAR. 3.59.<BR>(Cf. hib. fiod f. frigus, fuar frigidus, quae, si huc<BR>pertinent, gutturalem in labialem converterunt.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=133-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3353" target="_blank">Correction</a>

