जम्बुद्वीप
जम्बुद्वीप m. (e जम्बु et द्वीप m. insula, paeninsula) India<BR>(*). N. 26.37.<BR>(*) Wils.: Jambu Dwîpa, said to be so named from<BR>the preceding plant abounding in it, and implying according<BR>to the Purana's, the central division of the world<BR>or the known world: according to the Bauddha's it is<BR>confined to India.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=135-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3384" target="_blank">Correction</a>

