जृम्भ् 1. A. (scribitur जृभ्, gr. 110^a).)<BR>1) id. H. 2.6.: जृम्भमाण;<BR>PAR. BHAR. 3.4.: {#tfzRe jfmBasi pApakarmanirate<BR>nA 'dyA 'pi santuzyasi#}.<BR>2) laxare arcum. R. Schl. I.75.17.:<BR>तदा तु जृम्भितं शैवन् धनुर्…हूङ्कारेण;<BR>19.: जृम्भितन् तद् धनुर् दृष्ट्वा. V. जृभ्, जृम्भण.<BR>c. उत् hiare, aperire, se expandere. Lass. 69.5.: {#vasantaH<BR>santato 'jfmBetAnaNgaSfNgAraH#}.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम् conari, contendere. BHAR. 2.6.: {#vyAlam<BR>bAlamfRAlatantuBir asO rodDum ujjfmBate#}.<BR>c. वि hiare, se expandere; diffundi, dispergi. UR. {#rajanyAm<BR>vijfmBate madanavADA#}; RAGH. 3.19.: {#suKaSravA<BR>maNgalatUryanisvanAH…vyajfmBanta#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=141-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3510" target="_blank">Correction</a>

