तक्ष्
तक्ष् 1. et 5. P.<BR>1) frangere, dissecare, findere. MAH. 3.1585.:<BR>शरैस् ततक्षाते परस्परम्; 4.1883.: {#anyonyan<BR>tatakzur izuBiH#}.<BR>2) in dial. Vêd. facere, fabricari.<BR>RIGV. 32.2.: त्वष्टा ऽस्मै वज्रं स्वर्यन् ततक्ष<BR>«Tvashtris ei telum laude dignum paravit»; 20.2.;<BR>52.7.; 61.6.; 111.1. (Lith. taszau dolo, ascio;<BR>russ. tesatj dolare; polon. ćieśla faber lignarius, v. sq.;<BR>lat. tig-num, cf. Pott. I.270.; boruss. vet. tikint facere,<BR>tikinnimai facimus, teikusna creatio, creatura; gr.<BR>ΤΕΚ, τίϰτω, τέϰνον, τεύχω.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=146-3a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3597" target="_blank">Correction</a>

