तडाग n. piscina, lacus. N. 12.8.; 13.2.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=147-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3610" target="_blank">Correction</a>

