तडित्वत् (a praec. s. वत्) fulmine praeditus. UR. 9.18.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=147-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3612" target="_blank">Correction</a>

