तथा
तथा (e stirpe pronom. त, s. था) sic, ita. DR. 4.1.; tam.<BR>H. 3.3. A. 7.13. — Particula assentiendi ita, vero, sane.<BR>H. 4.59. SU. 3.22. Repetitum respondet ad यथा यथा<BR>(quomodocunque). N. 8.14. — तथा ऽपि nihilominus,<BR>tamen. HIT. 11.5. 15.10.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=148-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3629" target="_blank">Correction</a>

