तदा Adv. (a stirpe pronom. त s. दा) illo tempore, tunc.<BR>H. 1.15. — Respondet ad यदा quando. BH. 2.52. 4.7.<BR>DR. 5.18. — Saepe redundat, ubi in narrationibus eventus<BR>tempus definit, quod jam aliis temporis adverbiis sufficienter<BR>indicatum est. H. 1.30. N. 20.3. — In apodosi<BR>post यदि valet nostrum s o. Lass. 7.13.: {#yady ezA mama<BR>BAryA Bavati tadA jIvAmi#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=148-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3633" target="_blank">Correction</a>

