तनय m. (r. तन् s. अय, cf. सन्तान) filius. N. 13.34.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=148-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=3639" target="_blank">Correction</a>

