दल्
दल् 1. P. findi. BHATT. 14.20. 99.: ददाल भूः; GITA-GOV. 7.35.:<BR>दलति सा हृदि विरहभरेण. — Caus.<BR>vel cl. 10. दलयामि et दालयामि findere. BHATT.: {#muzwinA<BR>'dAlayat tasya mUrdDAnam#}; BHAR. 2.36.: {#hetidalito<BR>nAgaH#}. (Cf. दॄ i. e. दर्, unde दल् mutato र् in ल्;<BR>lith. dalis pars v. दल, dallykas pars, fragmentum, daliju<BR>divido; goth. dails pars; germ. vet. tail, teil; tîlô deleo,<BR>tîligô id. = दलयामि, mutato य् in g (gr. comp. 109^a).<BR>6);<BR>lat. dolo; hib. dail «a share, portion», dailim «I give,<BR>deal out» (nisi haec pertinent ad दा, ददामि, unde dailim<BR>mutato d in l ortum esse posset), duil «partition,<BR>distribution», duillean «a spear», duillean «a pin, thorn».)<BR>c. वि findi, diffindi. NAIṢ. 4.88.: {#tvadizuBir vyadalizyad<BR>vajro 'pi#}.<BR>c. वि praef. अन्तर् Caus. vel cl. 10. diffindere, dilacerare.<BR>BHAR. 2.77.: कठिनदृषदन्तर्विदलितः.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=164-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4011" target="_blank">Correction</a>

