2. दा 2. P. (लवने K. लूने V.) desecare, abscindere, decidere.<BR>(Cf. दो, दल्; gr. δαίομαι, δαίς, δαΐζω, nisi<BR>pertinent ad दा dare; cambro-brit. de «to part, to separate»;<BR>Adj. «separate, parted, divided»; dead «a parting,<BR>separation».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=167-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4030" target="_blank">Correction</a>

