दीर्घ
दीर्घ (r. दृह् crescere s. अ, mutato ह् in घ् sicut in मेघ a<BR>मिह्; cf. Pott. Lass. et Benfey I.98.) longus, de spatio<BR>et tempore. SA. 2.27. UR. 37.18. (Fortasse e दार्घ attenuato<BR>आ in ई; Zend. darĕgha (v. Vocalismus p. 186.);<BR>gr. δολιχός, mutato ϱ in λ, insertâ vocali auxiliari, ενδελεχής;<BR>russ. dolog longus, dolgà longa = दीर्घा, dolgo<BR>n.; lith. ilga-s, abjecto d, iʃz-drykeṅs, iʃz-drykếlis<BR>«lang-gewachsen», v. Ruhig s. v. lang; fortasse<BR>etiam lat. longus et nostrum lang huc pertinent, abjectâ<BR>syllabâ initiali; Benfeyus l. c. huc refert lat. in-dulgeo.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=171-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4116" target="_blank">Correction</a>

