दु
1. दु 5. P.<BR>1) vexare, dolore afficere, contristare. RAGH. 8.54.:<BR>मुखन् तव विश्रान्तकथन् दुनोति माम्;<BR>19.21.: प्रणयिनीः सो ऽदुनोत्; MAH. 3.16192.: {#aNgAni<BR>me dunotu makaraDvajaH#}.<BR>2) intrans. vexari, dolore affici,<BR>dolere. MAH. 3.10069.: {#dunoti cittaM yadi tan na<BR>paSye#}; GITA-GOV. 3.: मन्मथेन दुनोमि. (Lith. dowiu<BR>vexo pertinet ad formam caus. दावयामि; gr. ὀ-δύνη, ὀ-δυνάω;<BR>de δύω v. 2. दु; fortasse lat. doleo e doveo, v.<BR>gr. comp. 20.; hib. leirim «I pain, torment» aut huc, i. e.<BR>ad Caus. दावयामि, aut ad दरामि - v. दॄ - pertinere<BR>videtur.)<BR>c. आ A. vexari, angi, dolore affici. MAH. 1.3289.: {#ADunvasva,<BR>vidunvasva#} pro आदुनुष्व, विदुनुष्व, adjecto charactere<BR>1^mae classis, sicut saepe in linguâ zend. (gr. comp. 519.)<BR>c. वि A. id. v. praec.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=171-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4120" target="_blank">Correction</a>

