धे
धे 1. P. bibere. MAN. 4.59.: न वारयेद् गान् धयन्तीम्;<BR>MAH. 3.10452.: धास्यति किम्; 10453.: {#mAm ayan<BR>DAsyati#}; NALOD. 2.11.: मधु नानाविधम् अधयत्.<BR>(Cf. दधि; slav. dojû mulgeo; lith. dế-lế sanguisuga;<BR>goth. daddja lacto, mammam praebeo; gr.<BR>ϑῆσαι, ϑῆσϑαι, ϑηλή, ϑῆλυς, τίτϑη, ϑοίνη; germ. vet. tuta,<BR>tutta mamma (nostrum Zitze), cujus syllaba reduplicativa<BR>respondet sanscrito द in praet. redupl. दधौ (a धा,<BR>v. gr. min. 353.), attenuato अ in u; hib. daif f. «drink»<BR>fortasse forma redupl. cum f pro ध् sicut e. c. in lat. fumus<BR>= धूम, v. gr. comp. 11.).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=186-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4412" target="_blank">Correction</a>

