नभस्
नभस् n. (ut videtur, e न et भस् pro भास्, ita ut proprie significet<BR>non splendens, sicut nubes dicitur नभ्राज्, cf.<BR>A. Benary p. 229.) n. aër, coelum. IN. 1.3. H. 3.6. SU. 6.19.<BR>BH. 11.24. (Slav. nebo id., them. nebes, gen. nebes-e,<BR>v. gr. comp. 264.; gr. νέϕος, νέϕε(σ)-ος, v. gr. comp. 128.;<BR>lat. nubes, nebula; germ. vet. nibul nebula; lith. débesis<BR>nubes, mutatâ nasali in mediam ejusdem organi sicut<BR>in dewyni novem, gr. comp. 317.; hib. neamh «heaven»;<BR>cambro-brit. nev.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=190-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4493" target="_blank">Correction</a>

