पत्र n. (etiam पत्त्र, r. पत् s. त्र)<BR>1) ala.<BR>2) folium.<BR>3) (r.<BR>पद्) currus. RAGH. 15.48. (Gr. πέταλον, πτίλον.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=206-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4863" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पत्रिन्
पत्रिन् m. (a praec. s. इन्)<BR>1) avis. RAGH. 11.29.<BR>2) sagitta.<BR>RAGH. 3.53.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=206-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4864" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पथ्
1. पथ् 1. P. ire. (Cf. पद् et पथिन्.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=206-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4865" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पथ्
