पय्
पय् 1. P. A. (गतौ) ire.<BR>c. वि sternere. (in dial. Vêd. nisi विपयामि cohaeret<BR>cum rad. वप्, attenuato अ in इ). RIGV. (v. Westerg.)<BR>विपयन्ति वर्हिः. (Schol. स्तृणन्ति.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=209-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4890" target="_blank">Correction</a>

