पयस् n. (r. पी bibere s. अस्)<BR>1) aqua. MEGH. 23. 25. 41.<BR>2) lac.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=209-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4892" target="_blank">Correction</a>

पयोद
