परस्पर
परस्पर (e परस् - nom. sing. masc. hac in compositione<BR>Fem. et Neut. vice etiam fungente, servato स् ante प्<BR>secundum r. 79. - et पर, quod hac in compositione in<BR>obliquis sing. casibus solnm usurpatur) i. q. अन्योन्य<BR>q. v. H. 4.36. SU. 4.15. N. 13.14. BH. 3.11. 10.9. M. 35.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=210-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4918" target="_blank">Correction</a>

परा
परा (fortasse a पर alius sicut दक्षिणा a दक्षिण) Praep.<BR>insep. retro. (Cf. gr. παϱά; lith. par (praep. insep.) retro,<BR>e. c. par-wadinu revoco, par-eimi redeo; hib. frea-,<BR>far- e. c. freagaraim «I answer», far-bhuille «a backblow»,<BR>v. Pictet p. 89. Fortasse etiam lat. re-, osset.<BR>ra- huc pertinent, abjectâ syllabâ initiali. E goth. linguâ<BR>fair- huc retulerim, attenuato a in i, praefixo a, v.<BR>gr. comp. 82.; germ. vet. far, fir; nostrum ver, v.<BR>Grimm III.256.4. c.; etiam faur pro e परा ortum esse<BR>potest, abjecto आ finali, attenuato a medio in u; germ.<BR>vet. furi; nostrum für; island. vet. fyri, attenuato आ in<BR>i; v. परि.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=210-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4919" target="_blank">Correction</a>

