पराक्रम m. (r. क्रम् ire praef. परा s. अ) vis, robur, fortitudo.<BR>H. 2.36.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=210-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4920" target="_blank">Correction</a>

