परि
परि Praep. insep. circum; in comp. cum adjectivis valde, v.<BR>परिलघु, परिशुष्क. (Gr. πεϱί; hib. faoi «about, around»<BR>ejecto r; germ. vet. furi, island. fyri, nostrum für huc<BR>referri possent, nisi इ finale in linguis germanicis ubique<BR>evanuisset, quam ob rem vocalem i hujus praepositionis<BR>ab â formae परा deduxerim, quod primum in a breve,<BR>deinde, quod saepissime accidit, in i se attenuaverit. De<BR>lat. et lith. per v. पार.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=210-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=4934" target="_blank">Correction</a>

