2. पश् 4. P. (in tempp. specialibus tantum usurpatur et a<BR>grammaticis Indicis in radices non receptum est)<BR>videre, v. दृश्. (Hib. faicim «I see», feachaim «I look,<BR>view», faochog «oculus»; lat. specio, praefixo s, fortasse<BR>e praep. सम्, nisi पश् corruptum e स्पश्, v. 1. पश्;<BR>germ. vet. spêho speculor; gr. σκέπτω, mutatâ lab. in<BR>gutt. et vice versâ, v. Pott. p. 267.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=213-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5036" target="_blank">Correction</a>

