प्सान
प्सान n. (r. प्सा s. अन) cibus. AM.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=235-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5620" target="_blank">Correction</a>

फकक्
फकक् 1. P. (नीचैर्गतौ K. असद्व्यवहारे शनैर्गतौ V.)<BR>repere, tarde incedere, improbe agere.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=235-1a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5621" target="_blank">Correction</a>

फण्
फण् 1. P. (गतौ) ire, se movere. — Caus.<BR>1) फणयामि<BR>facere ut alqs se moveat.<BR>2) फाणयामि pingue lactis<BR>auferre. K.: फाणयति दुग्धम् «he skims the milk».<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=235-1a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5622" target="_blank">Correction</a>

फण
