1. बर्ह् vel वर्ह् 1. et 10. P. (वधे दीप्तौ) ferire, occidere,<BR>lucere. Cf. वृह्, बल्ह्.<BR>c. नि in dial. Vêd. prosternere. RIGV. 100.18.: {#dasyUn…<BR>hatvA pfTivyAM SarA nibarhIt#} «hostes feriendo humi<BR>tela prostravit».<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=237-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5674" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ह्
2. बर्ह् vel वर्ह् 1. P. (स्मृतिहिंसादानवाक्षु) meminisse;<BR>ferire, laedere, occidere; dare; loqui. Cf. {#vfh,<BR>balh#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=237-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5675" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बर्ह्
