बल्
1. बल् 1. P. (धान्यावरोधे K. धान्यावरोधे जीवने V.)<BR>opulentiam, fortunam alcjs impedire, perturbare;<BR>vivere.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=237-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5677" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्
2. बल् 1. A. (दानवधनिरूपेषु) abscindere (दान a दो?);<BR>ferire, occidere; explorare, investigare. Cf. भल् 1. A.,<BR>बिल्, भिल्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=237-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5678" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्
3. बल् 10. P. बालयामि (भृतौ K.) sustentare, nutrire. K.:<BR>बालयति बालम् पिता. (Cf. भृ i. e. भर्.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=238-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5679" target="_blank">Correction</a>

बल्
