बल
बल (r. बल् s. अ)<BR>1) n. vis, robur. IN. 4.8. H. 4.14.<BR>2) n. exercitus.<BR>N. 2.11. 17.22.<BR>3) m. nom. pr. Daityi, quem Indrus<BR>occidit. (Cf. lat. valor, validus, valeo, cum praep. de:<BR>debilis.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=238-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5681" target="_blank">Correction</a>

