बाल
बाल m. (r. 3. बल् nutrire s. अ)<BR>1) puer, parvulus, infans.<BR>Collective, in Plur. vel initio compos. pueri, parvuli, infantes<BR>utriusque sexus. BR. 1.28. 3.7. N. 12.123. SA. 2.8.<BR>2) pilus.<BR>3) cauda. RAGH. 9.66. MEGH. 54. — Adj.<BR>infans, aetate parvus, juvenis, novus, novellus, recens.<BR>UR. 75.13.: बालम् इवे ऽन्दुम्; RAGH. 3.22.: बालचन्द्रमाः;<BR>SAK. 8.9.: बालविटपिभ्यः. (Lith. wála-s<BR>pilus caudae equi. V. sq.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=238-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5709" target="_blank">Correction</a>

