ब्रह्मचर्य
ब्रह्मचर्य n. (e ब्रह्मन् et चर्य, quod seorsum non invenitur<BR>et vitae rationem significare videtur, a चर् ire, facere<BR>suff. य) castimoniae vel coelibatus votum, castimonia.<BR>IN. 4.10.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=240-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5747" target="_blank">Correction</a>

