ब्राह्म (fem. ई, a ब्रह्मन् s. अ, v. gr. 651.) brahmicus, ad<BR>deum Brahmam pertinens. BH. 2.72.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=241-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=5753" target="_blank">Correction</a>

