मध्य
मध्य Adj. medius. Subst. m. n.<BR>1) medium. SA. 2.1.<BR>2) medium<BR>corpus (Anglis waist). IN. 5.9. (Lat. medius, medium;<BR>goth. MIDJA, nom. m. midji-s, v. gr. comp. 287.<BR>annot. 7.; hib. meadhon «the middle, midst, centre»; gr.<BR>μέσσος per assim. e μεσϳος pro μεδϳος; lith. widdurys<BR>medium, mutato m in w, widdù naktis media nox; serv.<BR>medju; slav. междю meschdju inter.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=256-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6041" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मध्यतस्
मध्यतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) in medio. H. 1.21.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=256-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6042" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मध्यम
मध्यम<BR>1) Adj. medius.<BR>2) Subst. m. n. medium corpus,<BR>the waist. N. 1.10. (Goth. MIDUMA, midums medius.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=256-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6043" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मध्यमलोक
मध्यमलोक m. (e praec. et लोक) medius mundus i. e.<BR>terra, quippe quae inter coelum et infernum. UR. 92.2.<BR>(Cf. goth. midjun-gards id., ad literam: media domus,<BR>medius hortus.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=256-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6044" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मन्
1. मन् 4. et 8. A. मन्ये, मन्वे, praet. mltf. अमंसि, fut.<BR>aux. मंस्ये.<BR>1) cogitare. N. 1.21.: {#yaTA tvad<BR>anyam puruzan na sA maMsyati karhicit#} (ubi PAR.<BR>metri causâ).<BR>2) putare, credere, opinari. N. 5.12.: {#yaM<BR>yaM hi dadfSe tezAn tan tam mene nalan nfpam#}; 16.:<BR>शरणम् प्रति देवानाम् प्राप्तकालम् अमन्यत; 19.18.:<BR>यान् अन्यान् मन्यसे ब्रूहि तान्; 19.: {#yAn manyase<BR>samarTAMs tvam#}; H. 4.19.: बलिनम् मन्यसे यच्च आत्मानम्;<BR>GITA-GOV. 4.11.: {#stanavinihitam api<BR>hAram udAraM sA manute kfSatanur iva BAram#}; A. 5.17.:<BR>मन्वाना देवराजम् माम्. Absol. HIT. 75.7.: {#manye<BR>durjanacittivfttiharaRe DAtA 'pi BagnodyamaH#}. Notetur<BR>formula यदि मन्यसे si putas, si ita tibi videtur, si<BR>tibi libuerit, e. c. N. 5.3.: {#damayantyAH paRaH sADu vartatAM<BR>yadi manyase#}; 16.34.: ताम् वेत्थ यदि मन्यसे.<BR>3) aestimare. Lass. 12.15.: {#jIvaYca puruzaviSezAMSca<BR>sImantinyas tfRam iva manyante#}. — Part. pass.<BR>मत n. cogitatum, cogitatio, opinio. IN. 3.1. BR. 2.26.<BR>(Cf. म्ना, quod litteris transpositis e मन्, productâ vocali;<BR>goth MAN putare, man puto, pl. munum, Praes.<BR>cum formâ Praet.; ga-munan meminisse, v. मति; lat.<BR>memini, com-miniscor, moneo nititur formâ caus. मानयामि,<BR>prâcr. माणेमि, ita germ. vet. manôm, manêm,<BR>v. gr. comp. 109^a).6.; fortasse mando adjecto d sicut in<BR>goth. hunds canis = शुन्, v. श्वन्, ΚΥΝ v. ज्ञा praef.<BR>आ in formâ caus.; gr. μένος = मनस्; μῆτις = मति,<BR>cf. मत pro मन्त; fortasse μέλλω e μένϳω sicut ἄλλος<BR>= अन्य, μαίνομαι, μῆνις, v. मन्यु, μάντις; lith.<BR>menû recordor, pri-manùs prudens, intelligens; russ.<BR>mnju opinor; hib. muinim «I teach, instruct»; fortasse<BR>smuainim «I think, imagine, devise, consider» e मन्<BR>praef. सम्, nisi pertinet ad स्मृ i. e. स्मर् mutatâ liquidâ<BR>r in n.)<BR>c. अनु<BR>1) consentire, assentire, comprobare. MAN. 9.97.:<BR>यदि कन्या ऽनुमन्यते; R. Schl. II.2.13.: {#yad idam…<BR>mayA sADu sumantritam Bavanto me 'numanyantAm#}. C.<BR>न rejicere, repudiare. RAGH. 16.85.: {#imAM svasAraYca<BR>yavIyasIm me…nA 'rhasi nA 'numantum#}.<BR>2) veniam<BR>dare, c. acc. pers. R. Schl. II.21.45.: {#anumanyasva mAn<BR>devi gamizyantam ito vanam#}. — Caus. facere ut<BR>alqs assentiatur, comprobet. R. Schl. II.2.<BR>c. अभि<BR>1) opinari, credere. BHATT. 5.71.: {#aBimanye<BR>'han tvAM harantIM SriyaM SriyaH#}.<BR>2) assentiri, permittere.<BR>MAH. 1.5743.: {#aDarmyam idam atyantaN kaTam<BR>BIzmo 'numanyate vivAsyamAnAn asTAne nagare yo#}<BR>ऽभिमन्यते.<BR>3) appetere, desiderare. R. Schl. II.72.45.:<BR>कच्चिन् न परदारान् वा राजपुत्रो ऽभिमन्यते; MAN. 10.95.:<BR>न ज्यायसीं वृत्तिम् अंभिमन्येत.<BR>c. अव spernere. H. 3.10.: {#mA 'vamaMsTAH pfTuSroRi matvA<BR>mAm iha mAnuzam#}; MAN. 4.135. 8.84. Pass. HIT. 56.12.:<BR>स सर्वैर् अवमन्यते.<BR>c. अव praef. अभि id. MAN. 4.249.<BR>c. वहु magni aestimare (v. gr. 653.). IN. 4.15.: {#sammAnam<BR>bahumanyaca#}; N. 15.13.: बहुमता नारी; MAH. 3.747.:<BR>न जीवितम् बहुमन्ये.<BR>c. सम्<BR>1) cogitare, putare. सम्मत n. assensus, consensus.<BR>N. 13.5. SA. 1.23.: {#prApte 'yan devakanye 'ti dfzwvA<BR>sammenire janAH#}.<BR>2) magni aestimare, honorare.<BR>सम्मत magni aestimatus, honoratus. IN. 1.11. 4.8. BR. 2.25.<BR>DR. 4.6.<BR>3) respicere, rationem habere, observare,<BR>curare. R. Schl. II.38.15.: {#mayA vihInAm…adfzwapUrvavyasanAm<BR>BUyaH sammantum arhasi#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=256-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6045" target="_blank">Correction</a>

मन्
2. मन् 1. P. (अर्चे V.) honorare. Cf. मान्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=257-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6046" target="_blank">Correction</a>

