2. मा 3. P. A. sonare. RIGV. 38.8.: वाश्रे ऽव विद्युन् मिमाति<BR>«mugientis instar vaccae fulmen sonat».<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=262-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6167" target="_blank">Correction</a>

