1. मुष् 9. P. furari, rapere. N. 5.7.: {#muzRantI praBayA rAjYAY<BR>cakzUMzica manAMsica#}; H. 42.12.: {#mahatA Bayena<BR>muzitaH#}. Cum acc. pers. RIGV. 93.4.: {#amuzRItam<BR>avasam paRiN gAH#} «cripuistis alimentum Pani, nempe<BR>vaccas». — मुष् cl. 4. v. मुस्. (V. मूष्, मूष.)<BR>c. परि furtum alicui facere, c. acc. pers. MAH. 3.13030.:<BR>अन्योन्यम् परिमुष्णन्तो हिंसयन्तश्च मानवाः.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=268-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6296" target="_blank">Correction</a>

