यकृत्
यकृत् n. (in casibus debil. etiam यकन्, v. gr. 205.) jecur.<BR>(Lat. jecur; gr. ἧπaϱ(τ), ἧπα(ϱ)τ-ος, mutatâ gutt. in<BR>lab.; germ. vet. lebara, lebera f., mutatâ sem. य् in ल्,<BR>v. gr. comp. 20., Graff. 2.80.; slav. jatra neut. pl.; huc fortasse [Page273-1b+ 6]<BR>etiam scot. cruthan pertinet, abjectâ syllabâ initiali.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=273-1a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6420" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्ष्
यक्ष् 10. A. (पूजायाम् K. महि V., ut mihi videtur, a यज्<BR>adjectâ sibilante) honorare, colere, venerari.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=273-1b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6421" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यक्ष
