यक्षी
यक्षी f. (a यक्ष signo fem. ई) Yakschia. N. 12.120.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6424" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यछ्
यछ् v. यम्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6425" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्
1. यज् 1. P. A. (in formis puris, Precativo A. excepto, nec<BR>non in syllabâ repetitâ praet. redupl., syllaba य corripitur<BR>in इ)<BR>1) colere deos. BH. 9.23.: {#ye 'py anyA<BR>devatA BaktA yajante…te 'pi mAm eva…yajanti#}.<BR>2) sacrificare. MAH. 1.4687.: {#asmiMSca yajamAne…upAgamaMs<BR>tato devAH#}; R. Schl. I.15.14.: {#lapsyase putrAn<BR>yadarTaM yajase#}. C. instr. sacrificii. SU. 2.13.: {#yajYEr yajanti<BR>ye kecid yAjayantica ye dvijAH#}; N. 5.45.: {#IjecA<BR>'py aSvameDena#}; 12.14.: अश्वमेधादिभिर् वीर क्रतुभिः…इष्ट्वा;<BR>36.38.: ईजेच विविधैर् यज्ञैः. Etiam<BR>c. acc. sacrificii. R. Schl. I.31.5.: यज्ञं यजमाने; 15.3.:<BR>अयजत् पुत्रीयाम् इष्टिम् पुत्रेप्सुः. C. acc. pers. R. Schl. I.14.7.:<BR>इष्टवान् अश्वमेधेन भवतः (cf. हु c.<BR>acc.).<BR>3) initiare, inaugurare. R. Schl. II.56.18. 21.: {#SAlAM<BR>yakzyAmahe#}<BR>4) dare. BHATT. 8.49.: यजन्तीभिः स्वविग्रहान्<BR>(Schol. ददतीभिः कामिभ्यः). — Caus. sacrificium<BR>alicujus peragere, de sacerdote. SU. 2.13.: R. Schl. I.10.26.:<BR>{#putrakAmam iman tAta tvaM yAjayitum<BR>arhasi#}. — Desid. sacrificare velle. MAH. 2.59.: यियक्षमाण.<BR>(Gr. ἅζω, ἅγιος = यज्य e यग्य, v. याग.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6426" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्
2. यज् (r. यज्) colens, adorans deos, in fine compos. BH. 7.23.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6427" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यजुस्
यजुस् n. (r. यज् s. उस्) nomen unius quatuor Vêdorum.<BR>BH. 9.17.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6428" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्ञ
यज्ञ m. (r. यज् s. न, v. euph. r. 93.) sacrificium. BR. 2.24.<BR>BH. 9.15. 20.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6429" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यज्वन्
यज्वन् m. (r. यज् s. वन्) sacrificator. IN. 1.16.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6430" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्
1. यत् 1. A. interdum P. operam dare, niti, studere, c. loc.<BR>vel infin. N. 15.4.: सर्वं यतिष्ये तत् कर्तुम्; 17.29.:<BR>नलस्या ऽऽनयने यत; 34.: यतध्वन् नलमार्गणे; H. 4.33.:<BR>अपनेतुञ्च यतितो नचै ऽव शकितो मम. — Absol.<BR>H. 1.4.: यतमाना वनं राजन् गहनम् प्रतिपेदिरे.<BR>(Cf. यस्, gr. ζητέω = Caus. vel cl. 10. यातयामि.<BR>Cum Pottio huc traxerim lat. nîtor = नि + यत्,<BR>ejectâ syllabâ य, vel correpto ya in i.)<BR>c. आ niti, inniti aliquâ re, pendere ex aliquâ re. HIT. 52.9.:<BR>स्वयत्नायत्तः; 48.7.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id., cum loc. MAH. 3.10484.: {#AsAm<BR>prARAH samAyattA mamacA 'trE 'kaputrake#}.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. N. 17.33.: {#prayatantu tava prezyAH puRyaSlokasya<BR>mArgaRe#}; 18.16.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6431" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्
2. यत् 10. P. (निकारोपस्कारयोः K. खेदोपस्करयोः V.)<BR>offendere, vexare; parare.<BR>c. निस्<BR>1) reddere, restituere. MAH. 3.16596.: {#tasmE tad<BR>Barato rAjyam…niryAtayAmAsa#}; 13182.<BR>2) condonare,<BR>ignoscere. MAH. 1.3018.: {#yamaH…tasya niryAtayati<BR>duzkftam#}.<BR>c. निस् praef. प्रति reddere. MAH. 3.13183.<BR>c. प्रति removere, abjicere, finire. MAH. 3.14728.: {#DArtarAzwravaDaN<BR>kftvA vErARi pratiyAtyaca#}.<BR>c. वि non condonare, punire, c. acc. pers. et rei. M. 1.3019.:<BR>तं यमः पापकर्माणम् वियातयति दुष्कृतम्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6432" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्
3. यत् (nom. यस्, या, यत्, gr. 272.) qui. DR. 2.5. 6.7. — Repetitum,<BR>quicunque. N. 5.12. BH. 3.21. — Antecedente<BR>vel sequente Relativo vi attractionis etiam notio<BR>aliquis per Relativum exprimitur (cf. locutiones ut<BR>कः कम् quis aliquem, v. किम्), e. c. HITOP. 20.60.:<BR>यो ऽत्ति यस्य यदा मांसम् qui alicujus; 53.2.:<BR>यद् एव रोचते यस्मै quod alicui; 17.9.: {#yad yena<BR>yujyate#} quo aliquid. Repetitum, HIT. 53.3.: {#yasya yasya<BR>hi yo BAvaH#} quae alicujus est natura. — Cum sequente<BR>को ऽपि quivis, quisque. N. 26.9. Cum sequente<BR>कश्चित् quicunque, wer irgend. SU. 2.13. — De constructionibus<BR>ut यस् त्वम् quia tu, यान् इमान् quia<BR>hos v. p. 39. s. v. इदम्. (Gr. ὅς c. spir. asp. pro य् sicut<BR>in ἅζω, ὑμεῖς, ὑσμίνη = यज्, युष्मे dial. Vêd.,<BR>युध्; lith. ji-s is pro ja-s, dat. ja-m = यस्मै, loc. ja-me<BR>= यस्मिन्; slav. i eum, jû eam, i-she qui, ja-sche<BR>quae; goth. ja-bai si, jau an. Huc etiam pertinet particula<BR>enclitica ei = î, quod cum demonstrativo conjungitur [Page275-a+ 37]<BR>ad exprimendum Relativum, e. c. saei qui, than-ei<BR>quem. V. gr. comp. 282. sq.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=274-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6433" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्
4. यत् Conj. (acc. neut. praec.)<BR>1) quod, daʃs. H. 1.5. 29. 2.4.<BR>BR. 3.16. In recentioribus scriptis etiam sicut gr.<BR>ὅτι, pers. keh ad introducendem orationem directam adhibetur.<BR>Lass. 45.5.: {#tvam mamA 'gra iti jalpasi yat<BR>tvAm vinA mamA 'nyA vallaBA nA 'sti#} (cf. यथा).<BR>2) quam ob rem, quâ de causâ. N. 24.18.<BR>3) quia. H. 4.14.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6434" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत
यत v. यम्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6435" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यतस्
यतस् Adv. (a stirpe Relativi य, v. gr. 272. suff. तस्)<BR>1) unde, relative.<BR>2) ex quo, de tempore, seitdem. R. Schl. II.7.1.:<BR>यतो जाता ex quo nata.<BR>3) ubi, relative.<BR>BR. 1.20.<BR>4) quo, quem in locum, relative. SA. 5.28.<BR>5) nam. HIT. 27.5. SAK. 53.16. (Gr. ὅ-ϑεν, slav. jûdû-sche,<BR>v. gr. comp. 421.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6436" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यति
यति m. (r. यम् cohibere, refraenare suff. ति) cujus animi<BR>appetitus cohibiti sunt, temperans. BH. 4.28.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6437" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यतिन्
यतिन् m. i. q. praec. (ut videtur, a यत cohibitum, refraenatum,<BR>suff. इन्). BH. 5.26.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6438" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्न
यत्न m. (r. यत् s. न) opera, nisus, studium. N. 1.6. 4.16. 9.36. 20.16.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6439" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्नतस्
यत्नतस् Adv. (a praec. s. तस्) studiose, diligenter. HIT. 30.22.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6440" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्र
यत्र Adv. et Conj. (a stirpe Relativi य s. त्र)<BR>1) ubi, relative<BR>H. 2.16. Interdum pro Locativo यस्मिन् ponitur, e. c.<BR>यत्र काले. BH. 8.23.<BR>2) quia. N. 11.7.<BR>3) quod, daʃs.<BR>N. 8.17.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6441" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यत्रक्वचन
यत्रक्वचन Adv. (e यत्र et क्वचन alicubi - a क्व suff. चन)<BR>ubicunque, quoquo versus. BR. 3.12.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6442" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथा
यथा (a stirpe Relat. य s. था)<BR>1) Adv. sicut. DR. 2.7. Repetitum,<BR>utcunque, quomodocunque. N. 18.14.<BR>2) Conj.<BR>ut. H. 4.51. SU. 3.21. N. 1.21.<BR>3) in recentioribus scriptis<BR>sicut यत् adhibetur ad introducendam orationem directam.<BR>UR. 13.4.infr.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6443" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथाकामम्
यथाकामम् Adv. (AVY. et यथा sicut et काम m. desiderium)<BR>ad arbitrium, ad libidinem, ex optato, ad voluntatem.<BR>IN. 4.18.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6444" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथातथम्
यथातथम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et तथा sic, quod hac in compositione<BR>Substantivi loco fungitur et veritatem significat,<BR>v. gr. 675.) secundum veritatem. IN. 5.52. N. 3.2. 16.39. 21.27.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6445" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथान्यायम्
यथान्यायम् Adv. (AVY. e यथा et न्याय m. convenientia,<BR>decentia, apta ratio) sicut convenientia, secundum convenientiam.<BR>IN. 1.21. BR. 1.26.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6446" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यथावत्
यथावत् Adv. (e यथा sicut et वत् sicut in fine compos.)<BR>apte, convenienter, congruenter. SA. 4.16. SU. 1.26.<BR>N. 6.8. 8.16. 24.44. 25.5.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6447" target="_blank">Correction</a>

