यदि
यदि Conj. (ut mihi videtur, a stirpe Relat. य suff. दि pro<BR>ति, cf. इति, nisi a neutro यत् adjecto इ)<BR>1) si. SA. 4.22. 5.97.;<BR>c. Potent. N. 17.44.<BR>2) an, num, germanice<BR>ob, e. c. H. 1.6.: न जानीमो यदि दग्धः पुरोचनः.<BR>(Fortasse gr. εἰ ex ἐδι.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=275-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6453" target="_blank">Correction</a>

यदिवा
