युध्
1. युध् 4. A. interdum P. (fut. aux. योत्स्ये, praet. mtf. अयुत्सि)<BR>pugnare. BH. 11.34.: युध्यस्व; DEV. 2.42.:<BR>अयुतानां शतैः षद्भिर्…युयुधे रणे; 43.: {#yudDe tasmin<BR>ayuDyata#}; MAH. 1.177.: न योत्स्ये; 3.15172.: {#yotsyanti<BR>…SatruBis tava#}. Cum acc. impugnare. MAH. 3.15175.:<BR>योत्स्यते केशवार्जुनौ. Pass. impers. HIT. 96.13.: {#yuDyate<BR>Buvi mAnavEH#}. Caus. योधयामि<BR>1) pugnare jubeo.<BR>MAN. 7.193.: {#dIrGAl laGUMScE 'va narAn agrAnIkezu<BR>yoDayet#}.<BR>2) impugno, c. acc. MAH. 1.3190.: {#yoDayAYcakrire<BR>surAn#}; 2.2120.: मा यूयुधो भारत पाण्डवेयान्.<BR>Desid. युयुत्से pugnare volo. MAH. 4.1252.:<BR>किमर्थन् न युयुत्ससे. (Hib. iodhna «spears, arms», v.<BR>आयुध; iodnach «valiant, warlike, martial»; iodhlan «a<BR>hero»; gr. ὑσ-μίνη, ὑσ-μίν e ὑϑ- sicut e. c. πέπεισ-μαι<BR>e πέπειϑ-μαι. Huc etiam trahi possent anglo-sax.<BR>gudh f., island. vet. gudh-r, gunn-r m., germ. vet.<BR>gund f. pugna, nisi pertinent ad हन्.)<BR>c. आ P. c. acc. impugnare alqm. DR. 5.7.: {#krudDam Ayotsyasi<BR>jizRum#}. — Caus. id. MAH. 3.15054.: {#AyoDitAstu<BR>ganDarvAH suciraM sodarEr mama#}.<BR>c. प्र Desid. pugnare velle. DR. 5.8.: {#yaH pARqavAByAm<BR>…prayuyutsase tvam#}.<BR>c. प्रति P. A. c. acc. impugnare alqm. BH. 2.4. MAH. 1.1703.<BR>— Caus. id. MAH. 1.7116.: {#ko duryoDanaM SaktaH<BR>pratiyoDayitum#}.<BR>c. सम् A. c. acc. impugnare. MAH. 1.5177. — Caus. id.<BR>MAH. 1.7098.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=282-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6523" target="_blank">Correction</a>

