युवन्
युवन् (ut videtur, pro द्युवन् abjecto द्, a r. दिव् vel द्यु<BR>splendere, sicut युत् = द्युत्; v. ओजस्. In casibus<BR>debilissimis यून्, fem. यूनी vel युवती, v. gr. 225.) juvenis.<BR>DR. 2.9. N. 12.123. (Lat. juveni-s, adjecto i,<BR>jûn-ior = correptae formae यून्; Lith. jauna-s juvenis;<BR>slav. jûn juvenis, jûnostj juventus; anglo-sax. iung, iong,<BR>geong juvenis; goth. juggs i. e. jung-s, them. jugga, e<BR>यून् adjectâ syllabâ ga; cambro-brit. ieuanc, ieuant juvenis,<BR>iau junior, ieuav natu minimus.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=282-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6532" target="_blank">Correction</a>

