रुकम n. (ut videtur, a r. रुच् e रुक्, servatâ primitivâ gutturali,<BR>sicut e. c. in वाक्य a वच् e वक्) aurum. HIT. 39.4.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=290-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6705" target="_blank">Correction</a>

