रुक्ष i. q. रूक्ष.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=290-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6706" target="_blank">Correction</a>

रुच्
1. रुच् 1. A.<BR>1) lucere, splendere. RIGV. 6.1.: {#rocante rocanA<BR>divi#} «fulgent fulgores ejus in coelo»; MAH. 1.6613.:<BR>{#ruruce sA 'Dikam suBrUr ApatantI naBastalAt<BR>sOdAminI 'va#}.<BR>2) placere. HIT. 53.2.: {#yad eva<BR>rocate yasmE Bavet tat tasya sundaram#}; MAH. 1.7442.:<BR>न रोचते विग्रहो मे. — रुचित n. libitum, gratum. SA. 5.80.:<BR>रुचितं यदि ते; MAH. 1.7952.: {#yad asya rucitaM<BR>kartun tat kuruDvam#}.<BR>3) approbare, gaudere. MAH. 1.7444.:<BR>विग्रहं तैर् न रोचे. — Caus. P. A.<BR>1) velle, cupere,<BR>appetere. MAN. 2.243.: यदि त्व् आत्यन्तिकं<BR>वासं रोचयेत गुरोः कुले (schol. इच्छेत्); R. Schl. I.36.3.:<BR>गमनं रोचयामास; MAH. 1.5741.: {#nahi pApam<BR>apApAtmA rocayizyati#}. (Cf. लोच्, लोक्, lat. LUC,<BR>luc-s; lûceo = Caus. रोचयामि - v. gr. comp. 109^a).6.<BR>gr. λευ-ϰός, λύχ-νος, goth. liuh-ath lumen, ubi iu respondet<BR>sancrito ओ = अ + उ, debilitato gunae incremento<BR>a in u - v. gr. comp. 27. - germ. vet. liuh-tjan<BR>lucere, nostrum leuch-ten; slav. Λоуча lûća radius,<BR>Λоуна lû-na luna; hib. loiche, loichead «a light, candle,<BR>lamp; lightning, flame, splendour», logha «splendid»,<BR>logh-mhar «bright». Huc etiam trahi possunt hib. leos<BR>«light», leosaim «I light up, kindle»; les «light, illumination»<BR>mutatâ gutturali in sibilantem, nisi pertinent ad<BR>लस्; v. लोक्.)<BR>c. अति P. splendore vincere, überstrahlen. MAH. 3.486.:<BR>अत्यरोचश्च भूतात्मन् भास्करं स्वेन तेजसा.<BR>c. अनु Caus. i. q. Caus. simpl. MAH. 3.12679.: {#vanam<BR>evA 'nvarocayat#}.<BR>c. अभि Caus. id. R. Schl. II.30.27.: {#na devi tava duHKena<BR>svagmi evA 'nurocaye#}. Cum infin. vel nomine actionis<BR>in अन R. Schl. II.29.19.: {#nA 'Birocayase netun tvam<BR>mAN kenE 'va hetunA#}; R. Schl. I.36.2.: गमनाया ऽभिरोचय<BR>(cf. गमनायो ऽपचक्रमे p. 87.).<BR>c. आ Caus. id. R. Schl. II.30.28.<BR>c. प्रति Caus. id. MAH. 3.11546.: प्रस्थानम् प्रत्यरोचयन्<BR>sie beliebten fortzugehen.<BR>c. वि splendere. N. 17.11.: {#piplus tasyA vyarocata…<BR>vyaBre naBasI 'va niSAkaraH#}; IN. 1.40.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=290-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6707" target="_blank">Correction</a>

