1. रुज् 6. P. frangere. रुग्न fractus. MAH. 3.678.: {#vAtarugna<BR>iva…vanaspatiH#}. — Cl. 10. (हिंसे) ferire, laedere,<BR>occidere. (V. रुजा, रोग aegritudo et cf. lith. láuźu<BR>frango, praet. láuźiau = Caus. vel. 10. cl. रोजयामि, mutato<BR>r in l, j i. e. g in ź v. p. 99. not.; germ. vet. LUCH<BR>vellere, ar-liuhhan evellere, v. Graff. II.137.; lat. lûgeo<BR>= Caus. vel. cl. 10. रोजयामि (gr. comp. §. 109^a).6.);<BR>gr. λυγϱός, ο-ΡΥΓ, ὀ-ϱύσσω, ὄ-ϱυγμα, ὀ-ϱυϰτή, ὀϱυχή,<BR>praefixâ vocali, sicut in ὄνομα, ὀϕϱύς, ἐ-λαχύς etc.)<BR>c. अव i. q. simpl. HID. 1.12.: अवरुज्य…गुल्मान्.<BR>c. आ A. id. MAH. 2.2113.: {#vizARaN gOr iva madAt<BR>svayam Arujate 'tmanaH#}.<BR>c. आ praef. सम् id. MAH. 4.1082.<BR>c. वि diffringere. SAK. 24.16.: धर्मारण्यं विरुजति गजः.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=291-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6711" target="_blank">Correction</a>

