रूप्
रूप् 10. P. (ut videtur, Denom. a रूप forma)<BR>1) formare.<BR>2) gestibus exprimere, indicare, repraesentare, proponere,<BR>oculis subjicere. SAK. 7.2.: रथवेगं रूपयति (v.<BR>नट्); UR. 21.11.<BR>c. नि<BR>1) facere, perficere, peragere. MAN. 6.38.: {#nirUpye<BR>'zwim#}.<BR>2) percipere, videre, animadvertere. HIT. 23.3.:<BR>छिद्रन् निरूप्य.<BR>3) considerare, reputare, perpendere.<BR>HIT. 10.3.: तन् निरूप्यताम्; 10.17.: {#tan nirUpayAmi<BR>tAvat#}.<BR>4) examinare, inquirere, explorare, investigare.<BR>HIT. 20.15.: {#pakziBir itas tato nirUpayadBis<BR>tarukoware SAvakAsTIni prAptAni#}; 90.1.: {#aham api<BR>gatvA kim etad iti nirUpayAmi#}. Pervestigare,<BR>perquirere, perscrutari. HIT. 68.14.: कोटरे निरूप्यमाणे.<BR>5) eligere, ausersehen. HIT. 41.2.: {#awavIrAjye<BR>'Bizektum BavAn…nirUpitaH#}.<BR>c. वि (Denom. a विरूप deformis) deformare. HIT. 65.1.<BR>R. Schl. I.1.44.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=294-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6738" target="_blank">Correction</a>

