वदन n. (r. वद् s. अन) os, vultus. N. 2.2. (Hib. aodann<BR>«the face», eudan «the forehead».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=307-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6992" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वदरी
