वदान्य
वदान्य (r. वद् s. आन्य)<BR>1) eloquens.<BR>2) munificus, liberalis.<BR>HIT. 77.20.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=307-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6994" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वध्
वध् P. interdum A. (caret tempp. special., scribitur etiam<BR>बध्)<BR>1) pulsare, ferire, tundere. MAH. 4.461.: अथै<BR>ऽनाम्…पातयित्वा पदा ऽवधीत्.<BR>2) occidere. R. Schl. I.2.18.:<BR>क्रौञ्चमिथुनाद् एकम् अवधीः; MAH. 1.4801.:<BR>शक्राज्ञया महाबाहुस् तान् वधिष्यति; 3.626.:<BR>तं वधिष्ये महीतले. (Cf. रध्, व्यध्, वाध्, बाध्, lat.<BR>laedo (v. Benary p. 49.); hib. faethaim «I kill», faethadh<BR>«killing», fesaim «I kill, destroy», feadhm «a battle».)<BR>c. नि occidere. MAH. 1.4121. 5472.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=307-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6995" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वध
वध m. (r. वध् s. अ, scribitur etiam बध) caedes. H. 1.46. 3.20.<BR>BR. 2.30.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=308-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6996" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वधू
वधू f. (scribitur etiam बधू, fortasse a r. बन्ध्)<BR>1) femina,<BR>etiam animalium femina. DR. 1.17.<BR>2) nurus. SA. 4.28. 6.9.<BR>3) femina affinis, fratria. SU. 4.15. (Hib. badhbh<BR>«an ill-inclined woman; a witch, a fary woman».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=308-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6997" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वधैषिन्
वधैषिन् (e वध caedus et एषिन् cupidus) caedendi cupidus.<BR>SU. 2.19.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=308-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=6998" target="_blank">Correction</a>

