1. वा 2. P. flare, spirare, de vento. N. 24.40.: {#vavOca pavanaH<BR>SuciH#}; A. 4.51.: शीतन् तत्र ववौ वायुः. - वात<BR>m. ventus. A. 11.12.; deus venti. H. 1.34. (Cf.<BR>वै; goth. VO flare, spirare (vaia, vaivô v. gr. comp. 617.),<BR>vinds, Them. vinda ventus; germ. vet. wa-dal flabellum,<BR>wat, wait, waiet, wahet flat; slav. vje-ja-ti flare, vje-tr<BR>ventus; lith. wếjas ventus; gr. ἄημι, ut videtur, ex ἀ-Ϝημι<BR>= वामि praef. आ, ἀήϱ; αὔϱα ex ἀϜϱα, οὖϱος ex ὀϜϱος;<BR>de αὔω v. वै; lat. ventus, aër aura; hib. bad ventus =<BR>वात, pers. bâd.)<BR>c. निस् extingui, de igne. SAK. 91.11.: {#nirvAsyataH pradIpasya<BR>SiKA#}. V. निर्वाण. — Caus. extinguere ignem.<BR>MAH. 1.1608.: {#samidDaY jAtavedasaM varzEr nirvApayizyAmo<BR>meGA BUtAH#}. — V. निर्वापन.<BR>c. प्र i. q. simpl. R. Schl. II.71.25.: प्रवाति पवनः श्रीमान्.<BR>c. सम् id. MAH. 4.1288.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=314-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7108" target="_blank">Correction</a>

