वृत्तान्त
वृत्तान्त m. (e praec. et अन्त finis)<BR>1) casus, eventus, res,<BR>res gesta, historia. N. 4.23. HIT. 72.17. UR. 86.4.infr.<BR>Lass. 9.9. 31.9.<BR>2) status, conditio. UR. 37.4. vid. sq.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=333-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7526" target="_blank">Correction</a>

वृत्ति
वृत्ति f. (r. वृत् s. ति)<BR>1) status, conditio, vitae ratio, versandi,<BR>agendi ratio. SA. 5.46. BH. 14.18. Lass. 39.13. 40.19.<BR>MEGH. 8. 91.<BR>2) victus. HIT. 36.21.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=333-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7527" target="_blank">Correction</a>

