श्
श् Haec littera orta est e क् et respondet graeco k, lat. c,<BR>lith. k et sz, slav. k et s, hib. c, ch et s; germ. h; v. gr.<BR>comp. §§. 21. 87.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=340-1a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7692" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्
1. शंस् 1. P. interdum A.<BR>1) dicere, indicare, narrare. N. 13.53.:<BR>शंस मे का ऽसि कस्य वा; 12.35.: {#nalaM<BR>yadi na SaMsasi#}; 12.126.: यदि जानीथ नृपतिङ् क्षिप्रं<BR>शंसत मे प्रियम्; R. Schl. II.68.8.: {#mAcA 'smE pitaram<BR>mftam BavantaH SaMsizuH#}; SU. 3.11.: {#sundopasundayoH<BR>karma…SaSaMsire#}.<BR>2) laudare. BH. 5.1.: {#punar yogaYca<BR>SaMsasi#}; MAH. 2.2298.: {#SaSaMsur drOpadIn tatra kutsanto<BR>DftarAzwrajam#}. (Cf. शास्. Fortasse lith. sakau<BR>dico, loquor, litteris transpositis e kasau; ita etiam germ.<BR>vet. sagên dicere, anglo-sax. sagan, sœgan, cum g pro<BR>h, quod pro श् = क् exspectaveris. Cf. etiam SANG<BR>canere (v. Graff. 6.91.). Pottius huc refert lat. cano<BR>(v. क्वण्), Cas-menœ, Ca-menœ, car-men. Cum शंस्<BR>conferatur etiam pers. خواندن kân-den recitare, cantare,<BR>nisi pertinet ad क्वण् vel स्वन्, v. gr. comp. 35.<BR>De خاستن kâs-ten cupere v. 2. शंस्.)<BR>c. अभि calumniari, conviciari, maledicere, objurgare, accusare,<BR>criminari; अभिशस्त increpatus. MAN. 8.116.:<BR>वत्सस्या ऽभिशस्तस्य पुरा भ्रात्रा यवीयसा; AM. III.1.43.:<BR>आक्षारितः क्षारितो ऽभिशस्ते; MAN. 2.185.: {#aBiSastAMs<BR>tu varjayet#}; 3.159.<BR>c. आ<BR>1) indicare. RAGH. 1.86.<BR>2) implorare. DR. 5.12.:<BR>आशंस…सौवीरराजस्य पुनः प्रसादम्.<BR>c. प्र laudare, celebrare. N. 1.16. 3.16.<BR>c. प्र praef. अभि id. A. 1.6.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=340-1b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7693" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्
2. शंस् 1. A. interdum P. (इच्छायाम् K. आशिषि V.; scribitur<BR>शस्, gr. 110^a).) cupere, desiderare, fausta<BR>precari. (V. शास् praef. आ et cf. pers. خاستن kâsten<BR>cupere, velle, rogare, خواهم kâh-em cupio etc., hib.<BR>sant «greediness, covetousness, cupidity, lust», santaighim<BR>«I desire, covet, lust» V. Pictet p. 64.; lat. censeo,<BR>v. praef. आ sgf. 3.)<BR>c. आ<BR>1) cupere, desiderare. MAH. 1.7148.: {#kurupravIrAn<BR>ASaMsamAnaH…jagAma tAm BArgavakarmaSAlAM yatrA<BR>''sate te kurupravIrAH#}; 3.17171.: {#yodDum ASaMsate nityam<BR>PAlgunena#}.<BR>2) sperare. BR. 1.29.: {#yayA dOhitrajA~l<BR>lokAn ASaMse#}; MAH. 3.13647.: {#ASaMsate hi<BR>putrezu pitA…yaSaH#}. Cum dat. MAH. 1.148.: {#nA ''SaMse<BR>vijayAya#}. Cum infin. R. Schl. II.12.70.: {#na…ciraY<BR>jIvitum ASaMse#}. ATM. DR. 5.5.: जेतुम् आशंससि<BR>धर्मराजम्.<BR>3) credere, putare, c. यदि. R. Schl. II.51.14.:<BR>{#kOSalyAcE 'va rAjAca taTE 'va jananI mama nA<BR>''SaMse yadi jIvanti#}; II.86.15.: {#nA ''SaMse yadi te<BR>sarve jIveyuH#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=341-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7694" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंसिन्
शंसिन् (r. शंस् s. इन्) dicens, indicans, nuntians. UR. 69.15.<BR>SAK. 46.15.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=341-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7695" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शंस्त्
शंस्त् 2. P. (scribitur शस्त्) dormire. Vid. 2. शस्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=341-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7696" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्
शक् 5. P. et 4. P. A. posse, valere. H. 1.6.: {#gantuYcE 'va<BR>na SaknumaH#}; R. Schl. I.20.4.: {#na hi Saknoti…samAptuN<BR>kratum#}; BR. 1.24.: {#na hi SakzyAmi kiYcana parityaktum<BR>aham banDum#}; 27.: {#parityaktun na SakyAmi<BR>BAryAm#}; 28.: कुत एव परित्यक्तुं सुतं शक्यामि; N. 11.6.:<BR>शक्यसे ता गिरः सत्याः कर्तुम् मयि; A. 3.31.: {#nacE<BR>'nam aSakaM hantum#}. Cum locat. abstracti in अन<BR>loco infin. R. Schl. I.66.19.: न शेकुर् ग्रहणे तस्य धनुषः;<BR>N. 7.10.: {#suhfdAn na tu kaScana nivAraRe 'Bavac<BR>Cakto dIvyamAnam#}. Participia in त sunt शक्त et<BR>शकित, quorum prius active cum sgf. potens, alterum<BR>passive usurpatur. BR. 2.8. N. 7.10. H. 4.33. — Pass.<BR>impers. MAH. 1.6678.: स्थीयतां यदि शक्यते. — Notetur<BR>Passivi usus in constructione cum Infin., quippe<BR>qui passivâ formâ careat, ita ut passivam vim verbo auxiliari<BR>exprimere necesse sit. Dicitur e. c. ना ऽऽहर्तुं शक्यते<BR>(N. 20.5.) quasi latine dicas afferre nequitur<BR>ad exprimendum non afferri potest. Part. fut. pass.<BR>शक्य saepissime in hujusmodi constructionibus invenitur,<BR>e. c. IN. 1.17. 2.4. H. 1.35. 47. Etiam part. praet.<BR>शकित. H. 4.33.: {#apanetuYca yatito nacE 'va Sakito<BR>mayA#}. Dicitur etiam शक्य pro जेतुं शक्य qui vinci potest,<BR>vincendus. DR. 5.12. — Desid. शिक्ष् correptum e<BR>शिशक्ष्, v. gr. 552. (V. शिक्ष् et cf. hib. ceach-t «power,<BR>eminence» = शक्ति, v. Pictet p. 63. Fortasse lat. co-nâri<BR>e coc-na-ri, ita ut ना respondeat characteri nonae<BR>classis et graeco νη in verbis ut δάμ-νη-μι; queo; cf. nequi-nont<BR>apud Fest. cum शक्-नुवन्ति; island. vet. hag-r<BR>dexter, hagna prodesse, hoegja moderare (Grimm. II.12. n. 96.);<BR>gr. ϰίϰυς; v. Pott. I.232. Benfey II.160.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=341-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7697" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकट
शकट m. n. currus. HIT. 24.8.: शकटम् (nom.).<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7698" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकटार
शकटार etiam शकटाल nom. pr. (Wils. «the minister of<BR>Nanda»). HIT. 61.20.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7699" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकल
शकल m. n. pars, portio, frustum. RAGH. 2.46.: शकलानि.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7700" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकन्
शकन् v. शकृत्.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7701" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकुन
शकुन m. (fortasse a r. शक् s. unâd. उन)<BR>1) avis species<BR>(Wils.: either the Indian vulture or the common kite-<BR>Falco cheela-; it is also applied to the Pondicherry eagle).<BR>N. 9.12.<BR>2) avis in universum.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7702" target="_blank">Correction</a>

