शकुनि<BR>1) i. q. praec. MAH. 3.10437.<BR>2) nom. pr. IN. 1.4.<BR>(Cf. lat. ciconia.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7703" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शकृत्
शकृत् n. (शकन् v. gr. 205.; fortasse forma redupl. cum {#Sa<BR>= ka#}, a r. कृत्) excrementum, stercus. (Fortasse gr.<BR>ϰόπϱος e ϰόϰϱος, lat. stercus, stercor-is fortasse per metath.<BR>e secort-is = शकृतस् e शकर्तस्; hib. seachraith<BR>«filth, dirt», cac «animal excrement», cacah «dirty,<BR>filthy», cacaim «I go to stool», lat. caco, gr. ϰαϰϰάω.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7704" target="_blank">Correction</a>

शक्ति
