शक्तु
शक्तु m. n. farina. (Wils.: According to some authorities<BR>only m. pl. (शक्तवः). The powder or flour of barley<BR>and other grain, first fried and then ground). HIT. 114.22.:<BR>शक्तुभूतः शारवः; 115.2. 7.: शक्तुशारव.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=342-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7706" target="_blank">Correction</a>

