1. शप् 1. P. A.<BR>1) A. jurare. MAN. 8.110.: {#vaSizWaScA 'pi<BR>SapaTaM Sepe pEyavane nfpe#} (Loc. pro Dat.); R. Schl. II.75.40.:<BR>{#SapaTEH kazwEH SapamAnam…Baratam…kOSalyA<BR>vAkyam abravIt#}. Cum instr. rei vel pers. per<BR>quam quis jurat. GHAT. 22.; R. Schl. II.21.16.: {#satyena<BR>DanuzAcE 'va dattene 'zwena te Sape#}; II.11.8.: {#tena rAmeRa<BR>kEkeyi Sape te vacanakriyAm#}; 34.47. 48.21. MAH. 1.5178.<BR>2) P. A. maledicere, exsecrari. IN. 5.48.: {#SaSApA<BR>'Ta DanaYjayam#}; N. 20.34.: कुपिता मा ऽशपत्; MAH. 1.4583.:<BR>तस्मात् त्वाम् अप्य् अहं शपे; 3.351.: {#putran<BR>te Sapsyate#}. — Absol. R. Schl. I.58.8.: {#SepuH paramasaNkrudDAS<BR>caRqAlatvaN gamizyasi#}. — Caus. शापयामि<BR>jurare jubeo. MAN. 8.113. (Fortasse शप् primitive<BR>dicere, loqui significavit, cf. शब्द sonus, quod fortasse<BR>e शप् + द dans; hib. cubhais «an oath», cubhas<BR>«a word, a promise», cab «a mouth».)<BR>c. अभि maledicere, exsecrari. R. Schl. II.49.48.: {#tvAm<BR>aBiSapsye 'haM suduHKam atidAruRam#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=344-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=7748" target="_blank">Correction</a>

