श्विन्द् 1. A. (scribitur श्विद्) i. q. श्वित्. (Cf. श्वित्, चन्द्.<BR>Huc vel ad चन्द् trahi potest island. vet. hita, hiti<BR>fervor, calor, heit fervidus, germ. vet. hiza, heiz, nostrum<BR>Hitze, heiʃs. Ad चन्द् etiam trahi potest lat. caleo,<BR>gr. ϰήλεος, mutato d in l.)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=360-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=8091" target="_blank">Correction</a>

