सन्धा f. (r. धा ponere praef. सम्)<BR>1) conjunctio.<BR>2) status,<BR>conditio.<BR>3) promissum, fides. Praesertim in comp.<BR>BAH. invenitur, Adjectivum सन्ध autem, quod Wilso affert,<BR>non existere puto; cf. उपमा.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=368-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=8246" target="_blank">Correction</a>

