सृप्
सृप् 1. P. ire, gradi. R. Schl. II.59.10.: {#naca sarpanti sattvAni<BR>vyAlA na prasarantica#}; HIT. 30.3.: {#satrAsam<BR>mandam mandaM sarpan (mUzikaH)#}. (Vid. सर्प et cf. lat.<BR>serpo, repo, gr. ἕϱπω, ϱ̔έπω. Huc etiam traxerim germ.<BR>vet. SLIF labi (slîfu, sleif, slifumês) per metath. e SILF<BR>= सर्प्, debilitato a in i, nostrum schleife, anglo-sax.<BR>SLIP, servatâ tenui (v. gr. comp. 89.). Fortasse germ.<BR>vet. SLICH repere, slichu, sleih, slichumês, mutatâ labiali<BR>in gutt.; lith. slenkiu repo, praet. slinkau, fut. slink-su; rếploju<BR>«ich krieche auf Händen und Füfsen»; hib. sleagaim<BR>«I sneak, drawl».)<BR>c. अप abire. MAH. 3.14112.: अपासर्पच् छणैर् भीतः.<BR>Aufugere. R. Schl. II.29.4.: {#sarve te tava rAGava rUpan<BR>dfzwvA 'pasarpeyuH#}.<BR>c. अप praef. वि id. MAH. 4.1899.<BR>c. उत् se extendere. N. 23.9.<BR>c. उत् praef. सम् ascendere. RAGH. 6.8.<BR>c. उप adire, aggredi. BR. 3.22.: {#prahasann iva sarvAMs<BR>tAn ekEkam upasarpati#}. Etiam ATM. R. Schl. II.96.9.:<BR>शिलान् ताम् उपसर्पत (omisso augmento).<BR>c. उप praef. सम् id. MAH. 1.6450.<BR>c. वि P. A.<BR>1) discedere, digredi, dispergi. N. 1.25.: {#haMsA<BR>visasfpuH sarvataH pramadAvane#}; MAH. 1.8286.<BR>2) vagari,<BR>volare, fluere. HIT. 10.1.: {#kapotarAjaH saparivaro viyati<BR>visarpan#}; MAH. 3.14997.: ऊर्ध्वम् आक्रममाणाः<BR>…विसर्पमाणाः (गन्धर्वाः); R. Schl. I.44.17.: {#vyasarpata<BR>jalam#}.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=381-b&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=8563" target="_blank">Correction</a>

