हाव
हाव m. (ut videtur, a r. ह्वे clamare s. अ, cf. gr. 449.) nugae,<BR>ineptiae, deliciae feminarum. (Wils.: Any feminine<BR>act of amorous pastime, or tending to excite amorous<BR>sensations, coquetry, blandishment, dalliance.). IN. 2.32.<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=400-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=8862" target="_blank">Correction</a>

