हिम (ut videtur, a r. हि, quod hac in formatione fluere significare<BR>videtur, suff. म, v. स्नु) Subst. m. nix, v. {#himavat,<BR>himAlaya#}. Adj. frigidus, v. हिमांशु. (Cf. slav.<BR>зима ζima hiems, lith. źiếma id., gr. χιών, χεῖμα;<BR>lat. hiems, hibernus; hib. geimhre, geimhrith, geimhreadh<BR>«winter», v. Pictet p. 66. et हिमऋतु apud Wils. ed. 2.;<BR>gamh «winter, cold».)<BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?cp=401-a&d=BOP" target="_blank">PDF</a><BR><a href="https://yaahi.github.io/?d=bop&e=8879" target="_blank">Correction</a>

